c: 34
v: 43
t: "When Our clear lucid verses (of the Qur´an) are recited, they say, \"He is just a man; he wants to distract you away from worshipping what your forefathers used to worship.\" They say, \"This is nothing but fantasy, a lie!\" When the (absolute) truth came to them, the unbelievers responded to it by saying, \"This is evidently nothing but magic"